         <div class="twelve columns">

            <h1>Jobs</h1>

            <hr />

            <pw>We are always happy to talk with game devs who are interested in a unique opportunity that is well-funded, 
            entrepreneurial, and focused on building a great culture. Big Huge Games is a company 
            that values team skills as much as technical skills, and we're committed to hiring only the best. By sticking 
            to this core value, we are creating a fun and energetic workplace with a passion for high quality game development. For more information, drop us a line at <a href="mailto:jobs@bighugegames.com">jobs@bighugegames.com.</a>
            </br>
            </pw> 
          </div> 
      </div>
</br>

